
COMMAND:
   blink 

ART:
   Blink allows a nun/monk to change her combat position any 3rd
   round during combat. The victim is then forced to do a wild
   attack, which drastically lowers the change of a hit.
   The durance of blinking depends on your condition.

COST:
    30 mentality points

POWER:
    dexterity/skilldependend 

PS: Tales are heared that even the breath of a dragon can be blinked out.

